<p>
  <span class="nym">Ahasuerus</span>
  <span class="gen">m.</span>
  
  <span class="etym"><span class="lang">Latin</span> <i>Assuerus</i> from <span class="lang">Greek</span> <i>Ξέρξης</i> from <span class="lang">Old Persian</span> <i>𐏋 </i> 'ruler' + <span class="lang">Old Persian</span> <i>𐎹𐎠𐎼𐏁𐎠</i> 'male, man'.
  </span>
  
</p>
  
<div class="usg">
  <p>The name of a king of Persia appearing in the Biblical book of Esther. Wycliffite Bible (1395): <i>Assuerus</i>. Sagradas Escrituras (1569): <i>Asuero</i>. Geneva Bible (1587): <i>Ahashuerosh</i>.</p>
</div>
  
  


